Twenty four hours after Floyd Mayweather Jnr dazzled the media with his skills , Manny Pacquiao takes his turn . The Filipino icon will be put through his paces at the iconic Wild Card gym in Los Angeles this evening under the watchful eye of trainer Freddie Roach . And after Mayweather was almost two hours late for his workout , Pacquiao has promised to be on time - and you can watch it here from 11 pm .